➜一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？
https://www.uisdc.com/cutout-software-evaluation	65734
<p>快到年底最忙的时候了，一波接着一波的项目需求就要向你砸来，大量的图片素材抠起来实在是耽误时间</p>
<p>​今天我给大家带来了感动所有设计师神器5个抠图工具大测评！！！看看到底哪个才是抠图工具中的好手快跟紧脚步~</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395030" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-1.jpg" width="812" height="600" /></span></p>
<p>本次测评我将围绕操作便捷度、抠图数量、抠图质量、网站功能、是否付费这5个维度来对这5个抠图神器进行测评~</p>
<p>PS:为了得到一个比较客观的结果，我们将使用三类图片进行测试</p>
<ul>
<li>普通背景的图片</li>
<li>边缘复杂的图片</li>
<li>有透明效果的图片</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395031" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-2.jpg" width="722" height="600" /></span></p>
<p>话不多说那就开始吧</p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">稿定抠图</span></h4>
<p>网站链接：<a href="https://koutu.gaoding.com">https://koutu.gaoding.com</a></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395032" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-3.jpg" width="966" height="528" /></span></p>
<p>稿定抠图首页这样滴~首页展示了三种主要的功能，分别为“批量抠商品”“批量抠人像”、“证件照换底色”可以说光看到这几个字眼，设计师们的泪水就要不争气地往下流了</p>
<p>下面我们来看看操作过程，首先将图片上传到网站中，点击图中上传图片，也可以直接拖拽或粘贴图片、输入图片网址进行上传。怎么样是不是很简单？然后会跳转到生成好的抠图页面</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395033" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-4.jpg" width="1000" height="625" /></span></p>
<p>这里能看到图片智能抠好的预览图如果不满意，还可以对图片进行手动修改</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395034" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-5.jpg" width="483" height="167" /></span></p>
<p>接着，网站还可以对图片进行自定义的调整</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395035" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-6.jpg" width="436" height="160" /></span></p>
<p>比如对图片质感进行自定义，说白了，就是添加喜欢的滤镜~</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395036" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-7.jpg" width="1000" height="625" /></span></p>
<p>还可以对图片背景进行更改、替换</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395037" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-8.jpg" width="1000" height="610" /></span></p>
<p>也可以将图片裁剪成自己想要的尺寸比例、对图进行旋转缩放等细节操作</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395038" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-9.jpg" width="1000" height="610" /></span></p>
<p>值得一提的是搞定抠图还能给图片添加阴影，可以说是太贴心了！</p>
<p>最后可以将自定义好的图片进行下载，搞定抠图提供了PNG与JPG的下载格式，满足不同场景的使用需求</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395039" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-10.jpg" width="1000" height="610" /></span></p>
<p>下面来看看效果</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395040" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-11.jpg" width="889" height="610" /></span></p>
<p>还不错，边缘自然不生硬，输出的图片质量为3000*2000，十分高清！！再来看看其他类型的图片抠出来的效果。</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395041" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-12.jpg" width="889" height="610" /></span></p>
<p>动物毛发边缘处理地稍微有些不自然，细小的地方被吃掉了</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395042" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-13.jpg" width="618" height="700" /></span></p>
<p>环境复杂的图片细节的处理会有一些小瑕疵，比如树叶之间和花瓣之间的区域不是那么细节可以手动调整一下</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395043" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-14.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>含有透明像素的图片抠图效果有些不自然~</p>
<p>测试到这里发现稿定抠图只免费提供5张图片的下载，想要抠更多的图片就要付费了，这里可以根据需要选择相应的服务</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395044" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-15.jpg" width="731" height="499" /></span></p>
<p>打分环节</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395045" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-16.jpg" width="682" height="700" /></span></p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">阿里妈妈</span></h4>
<p>网站链接：<a href="https://chuangyi.taobao.com/tools/santi?spm=a2esx.13162256.kbheader00.9.af184f2agRDCvz">https://chuangyi.taobao.com/tools</a></p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395046" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-17.jpg" width="966" height="528" /></span></p>
<p>听到名字就能知道是阿里旗下的网站</p>
<p>首页长这样~网站描述为「全自动高精度抠图，支持快速交互调整，擅长处理人物和电商商品」</p>
<p>下面来看看使用方法~首先根据图示上传图片然后会自动跳转到生成后的页面</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395047" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-18.jpg" width="877" height="387" /></span></p>
<p>边缘羽化有些过度了，但是整体效果还不错</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395048" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-19.jpg" width="877" height="463" /></span></p>
<p>网站也可以对图片进行手动修改有增加、去除背景的功能，也可以对背景进行自定义调整</p>
<p>在导出图片过程中时发现阿里妈妈支持PNG格式的下载</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395049" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-20.jpg" width="627" height="445" /></span></p>
<p>导出的图片素材为6100*4167，保留了原图片的尺寸大小，nice~</p>
<p>下面看看其他内容的图片</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395050" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-21.jpg" width="627" height="445" /></span></p>
<p>动物毛发处理地比较生硬，有些地方没有照顾到</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395051" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-22.jpg" width="492" height="700" /></span></p>
<p>在处理复杂背景图片上，阿里妈妈还挺粗糙的</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395052" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-23.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span>​</p>
<p>透明像素的背景处理效果还不错~打分环节</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395053" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-24.jpg" width="682" height="700" /></span></p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">Canva</span></h4>
<p>网站链接：<a href="https://www.canva.cn/create/remove-background/">https://www.canva.cn/create/remove-background/</a></p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395054" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-25.jpg" width="966" height="627" /></span></p>
<p>下面看看操作~点击“立即体验抠图功能工具&#8221;</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395055" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-26.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>会跳转到网站首页提示让你登陆，登陆需要点击“创建设计”上传图片</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395056" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-27.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>经历过稍微缓慢的加载过程后，在编辑页面选中图片</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395057" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-28.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>然后点击上方菜单栏中的「抠图特效」，再点击左侧列表中的「抠图」，才能进行抠图orz</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395058" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-29.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>过程也是有些缓慢</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395059" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-30.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>接着会出现抠好图片预览，就可以对图片进行自定义与下载啦~</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395060" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-31.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>canva提供了七种格式的免费下载，如Png、Jpg、Pdf、GIF等，但如果想要下载透明背景就要付费了，白嫖失败</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395061" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-32.jpg" width="1033" height="449" /></span></p>
<p>看看效果</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395062" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-33.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>后脑勺稍微有些煳掉了，整体效果还不错~</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395063" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-34.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>毛发有点小生硬，但好在还保留了一点细节处的毛发</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395064" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-35.jpg" width="500" height="700" /></span></p>
<p>复杂背景的处理也还不错~</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395065" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-36.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>打分环节~</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395066" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-37.jpg" width="682" height="700" /></span></p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">remove.bg</span></h4>
<p>网站链接：<a href="https://www.remove.bg/zh">https://www.remove.bg/zh</a></p>
<p>之前介绍过这个网站和它出品的插件：</p>
<p>[link https://www.uisdc.com/remove-bg]</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395067" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-38.jpg" width="966" height="531" /></span></p>
<p>国外组选手，根据首页提示上传图片</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395068" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-39.jpg" width="1243" height="700" /></span></p>
<p>图片生成时间很快，得到的图片质量也非常高清</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395069" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-40.jpg" width="709" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>网站的自定义的功能有对细节和背景进行调整两部分~然后就可以下载啦</p>
<p>网站提供了两种大小的图片进行下载612*408和6100*4067，但高清版本需注册支付后下载，所以如果对图片质量要求不高的话，可以直接进行选择像素低的版本的~</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395070" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-41.jpg" width="612" height="408" /></span></p>
<p>再来看看其他类型的图片对比</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395071" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-42.jpg" width="709" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>这里动物的毛发较前面相比比较是抠最好的，细节保留的比较完整~</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395072" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-43.jpg" width="574" height="700" /></span></p>
<p>背景复杂的图片很让人惊喜！说不上完美，但整体效果很不错了~</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395073" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-44.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>透明像素的图片效果也很透亮，这几位选手差距并不太大~，打分环节</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395074" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-45.jpg" width="682" height="700" /></span></p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">slazzer</span></h4>
<p>网站链接：<a href="https://slazzer.com">https://slazzer.com</a></p>
<p>之前介绍过：</p>
<p>[link https://www.uisdc.com/slazzer]</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395075" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-46.jpg" width="966" height="531" /></span></p>
<p>直接将图片拖拽或点击按钮就可上传到网站</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395076" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-47.jpg" width="709" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>网站反应速度也很快，也含有对背景调整这一自定义功能</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395077" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-48.jpg" width="709" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>最后下载时与remove.bg一样，有两种尺寸可以进行选择，有钱任性选择全尺寸，白嫖选择低尺寸就好~</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395078" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-49.jpg" width="563" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>本着白嫖原则下载的低尺寸</p>
<p>​<span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395079" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-50.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>最后看看其他类型的对比~</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395080" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-51.jpg" width="615" height="429" /></span></p>
<p>感觉动物毛发抠图国外组比国内组发挥要好~背景复杂组的发挥就不是很稳定了，看来还是要根据图片内容进行分析</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="一键抠图神器大测评，哪款才是当仁不让的C位选手？" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-395081" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uisdc-my-20201104-52.jpg" width="500" height="700" /></span></p>
<p>背景复杂组的发挥就不是很稳定了，看来还是要根据图片内容进行分析</p>
